Black has problems with his rook locked in the corner.} Nd7 ({Another option is
} 22... Qf8 23. Qf4 Kg7 24. f3 $1 e3 (24... exf3 25. Rxf3 $18) 25. Rfe1 Re8 26.
Rad1 h6 27. Rd3 g5 28. Qc7 Qe7 29. Qxe7 Rxe7 30. Rdxe3 Rxe3 31. Rxe3 Rd8 32.
