13. Nxc5 Bxc5 14. Bb5+ Kf8 15. Ng2 (15. Be2 Ng8 16. Nd3 Bb6 17. Nf4 Ne7 18. c4
$13) 15... Ng8 16. Nf4 Ne7 17. Qf3 Kg8 18. Bd3 Bd4 $15 {Bartel,M (2641)-Navara,
