Rxb7 Bxd1 13. Rxb8+ Kd7 14. Bxd1 Ne7 15. O-O $14) 10. Qxc2 Bxc2 11. Rb2 Ba4 12.
Nc7+ Kd7 13. Nxa8 Kc8 14. O-O Ba3 15. Rbb1 Bc2 $11) 8... Qxb1+ {Forcedly!
