 full control of the position.} Bg6 ({A high-profile game saw} 12... Qc7 {
which does not change the character of the position. White followed with} 13.
f4 Be4 14. c3 Bd3 15. Rf2 Nf5 16. Nxf5 exf5 17. Nb3 $16 {White has a big
